      "https://firsteducore.org/ontology#level": "low-concern",
      "https://firsteducore.org/ontology#notes": "Describes credentials and organizations — no learner PII. Published data is public by design. Organizations publishing to the Registry share institutional information voluntarily.",
      "https://firsteducore.org/ontology#dataClassification": "public"
    },
