      },
      "https://firsteducore.org/ontology#alignmentStatus": "full",
      "https://firsteducore.org/ontology#notes": "CTDL is credential-centric. Deep alignment with CEDS Credential entity including credential type taxonomy, issuing organizations, and requirements.",
