        "@id": "https://firsteducore.org/ontology#ceds-domain/competencies"
      },
      "https://firsteducore.org/ontology#alignmentStatus": "full",
      "https://firsteducore.org/ontology#notes": "CTDL models competency frameworks and their relationship to credentials. Credential Engine maintains CTDL-ASN for competency-specific vocabulary.",
