      },
      "https://firsteducore.org/ontology#alignmentStatus": "partial",
      "https://firsteducore.org/ontology#notes": "Badge criteria can reference assessment results. OB3 does not model assessment structure (test, session, item).",
      "https://firsteducore.org/ontology#gapNotes": "CEDS models full assessment lifecycle; OB3 only records the resulting achievement.",
      "https://firsteducore.org/ontology#cedsElement": [
