      },
      "https://firsteducore.org/ontology#alignmentStatus": "partial",
      "https://firsteducore.org/ontology#notes": "OB3 uses W3C VC identity (DIDs) for issuer and holder identification. Partial alignment with CEDS person identity elements.",
      "https://firsteducore.org/ontology#gapNotes": "CEDS Auth models full system access and role management — OB3 only handles credential identity.",
